sellerCard.oneLiner: Professional Software Developer Angular React Node MongoDB LLM Expert
sellerCard.description:
With over 12 years of hands-on experience in software development, I specialize in building scalable, high-performance applications from the ground up. I work with leading technologies such as ReactJS, Angular, NodeJS, MongoDB, MySQL, PostgreSQL, Kafka, and LLM ensuring efficient, modern web and backend solutions.

In addition to full-stack development, I offer comprehensive DevOps services:

Creation and management of Kubernetes clusters and microservices architecture.
End-to-end setup of CI/CD pipelines for seamless deployment.
Cloud infrastructure management.

description.content:
Professional Front-End Developer | Responsive Web Design | PSD to HTML/CSS


Are you searching for a skilled front-end developer to bring your website design to life with clean, responsive, and optimized code? Look no further!


With 10 years of experience, I specialize in HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap, JavaScript, and jQuery to build mobile-friendly and pixel-perfect professional websites. Whether you have a design in PSD, Figma, or another format, I will transform it into a fully functional website tailored to your needs.


My Expertise:

  • HTML5 & CSS3 for clean, modern code
  • Bootstrap for fully responsive designs
  • JavaScript & jQuery for dynamic functionality
  • PSD/Figma to HTML/CSS conversion
  • CSS Animations for an interactive user experience


Services I Offer:

  • Full website development from scratch
  • PSD to HTML/CSS/Bootstrap conversion
  • Custom CSS & JavaScript development
  • Mobile-friendly responsive design
  • E-commerce functionality integration


Why Choose Me:

  • Highly experienced in HTML/CSS, Bootstrap, and JavaScript
  • Real-time progress updates
  • Unlimited revisions until you're 100% satisfied
  • 24/7 customer support
  • 30 days of free post-delivery support


Lets build your dream website today! Order now!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What format can you work on for converting a design into responsive pages?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Figma, PSD, XD, AI, Sketch, PNG or JPG.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What about Revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well, client satisfaction is my responsibility, and I will revise the project to your satisfaction.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have some custom requirements. Can we still proceed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, sure. Just message me in conversation, and we will discuss everything. Ultimately, we will develop a website according to your requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you provide a responsive website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide you with 100% responsiveness on desktop, mobile, and tablet.
